{"tid":1629381,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"連儂牆應該貼下和理非行動手冊?","createTime":"2019-10-06T08:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:36:15.000Z","uid":254330,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de9535ed4e432c73c9e0a319d5818604c8d12a3c","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"係連登講野好多時都係打飛機,一黎post多唔係個個睇到,另外唔係個個(尤其係年紀大嘅)都睇,<span style=\"color: gold;\">搞到好多和理非唔知道應該點樣support行動緊嘅勇武</span><br />\n<br />\n上次仲見到有個婆婆拎左成箱麵包同紙包飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,結果佢地見冇人要,好失望；係裝修嘅時候仲係有和理非唔知應該點擔遮,唔係真係落雨咁擔呀!係要先遮cctv,然後再遮記者鏡頭呀!裝修進行緊嘅時候都要遮呀!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你點知個記者係咪<span style=\"color: red;\">香港01</span>?甚至<span style=\"color: red;\">人民日報</span>付國豪?<br />\n<br />\n同埋係<span style=\"color: gold;\">要有人睇水睇tg睇live map</span>,前晚好多勇武都係拎住各種遊戲道具,<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔得閒篤手機架</span>!<br />\n睇下班狗係咩位置,附近有咩突發情況,即刻講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以,我覺得應該要係連儂牆<span style=\"color: gold;\">貼下和理非行動手冊</span>,寫低<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>和理非<span style=\"color: gold;\">應該</span>做咩</ins></em><br />\n帶魔法液、帶玻璃樽、帶火槍、帶遮、帶後備tee、down live map、帶手套、帶濕紙巾、帶汽車維修員工具、係現場要睇資訊... 仲有其他請各位補充<br />\n<br />\n<em><ins>和理非<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該</span>做咩</ins></em><br />\nig打卡,打機,冇口罩,醫療物品唔洗買太多!fa每次都帶好多出去,再比只會增加佢地負擔! 帶數量極多嘅麵包 etc<br />\n重點! <span style=\"color: red;\">唔好聽到警車聲就走</span>! 人數夠係有得打! 另外,可能係救護/消防<br />\n唔好製造恐慌,有咩都要fact check先,因為好多次都有人叫有狗,結果乜都冇<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">散嘅時候,如果認為自己安全,帶走魔法液</span>！<br />\n101黃大仙就係冇帶走,結果AP不足,當然,安全係第一,如果係你走係走最前嘅,唔該你帶走部分物資<br />\n<br />\n之後貼係連儂牆,甚至係當日同和理非派發!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬需要大家比意見,之後會貼係連儂牆,同係現場派發<br />\n<br />\n另外,唔該全世界至少背定一個律師電話number!要背呀,記住<span style=\"color: gold;\">我冇野講</span>!"},{"pid":"2d31c30667fde4409801a7c7cc29759fdb5048ce","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CM8dBT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CM8dBT.png&h=231ec127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13e44d750179dc20b51c045d07ce04a70521e4e4","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"98190979!<br />\n帶魔法,帶手套,睇live map!"},{"pid":"dbda56bfcfd8369dac1bcd0ee53c0d8be7e83c3c","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"帶火槍,帶浮板"},{"pid":"0ad2f519ef72e8d60d9946b7d535c3eaef76b0f2","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"98190979"},{"pid":"e47f30109ddacc396f6f84d455c447863b725801","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"見到狗唔好退！人多有魔法嘅話夠打！"},{"pid":"7fb577773e363af713d20432af8c0c504abcfe9c","tid":1629381,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n仲可以善用<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>蟲系魔法</strong></span>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1823</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d2117d734c86d8fc72877497255c389012bd7069","tid":1629381,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3688e4cb869ff29d03b3c0b61f15a1a01357ac9b","tid":1629381,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"九八一九 零九七九<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9819 0979</span></span><br />\n<br />\n帶火槍(火機都得)、帶毛巾、帶長遮、帶手套"},{"pid":"5b1b50e220b5599c9fed25d8f85336cc44bc9023"